      <lg xml:id="TolE0201">
<l>ēḻa ṉurupiṟkut ticaippeyar muṉṉarc</l>
<l>cāriyaik kiḷavi yiyaṟkaiyu māku</l>
<l>māvayi ṉiṟuti meyyoṭuṅ keṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Words [denoting] direction,<note place="foot"><foreign xml:lang="ta">ticaippeyar,</foreign> e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">vaṭakku.</foreign></note></l>
<l>when followed by the seventh-case marker,</l>
<l>will not optionally take the empty-morph [<foreign xml:lang="ta">iṉ</foreign>] ;</l>
<l>there, the ending with the consonant is dropped.<note place="foot">Exx. : <foreign xml:lang="ta">vaṭakku + kaṇ &gt; vaṭakkaṇ</foreign> or <foreign xml:lang="ta">vaṭakkiṉkaṇ.</foreign></note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
